title: Even Angels Eat Beans 1973 | Action, Comedy Movie | Bud Spencer, Giuliano Gemma

sources.title: Even Angels Eat Beans 1973 | Action, Comedy Movie | Bud Spencer, Giuliano Gemma
sources.description:
Al Capone... Get lost! Dillinger... Phooey on you! Here come the funniest crooks since crime began!
Striving for a higher standard of living, a former ice-cream man and a wrestler convince a well-known mobster to hire them. However, they both soon realize that criminal life is not what they were looking for.

Original title: Anche gli angeli mangiano fagiol

Director: Enzo Barboni
Writers: Enzo Barboni, Tulio Demicheli, Marie Claire Solleville
Stars: Giuliano Gemma, Bud Spencer, Robert Middleton
Genres: Action, Comedy, Crime
